rules:
In `json` or `toon` mode, the command MUST output the `OverlapReport` structure:

```json
{
  "hasOverlap": true,
  "entries": [
    {
      "specId": "core:core/config",
      "changes": [
        { "name": "change-a", "state": "designing" },
        { "name": "change-b", "state": "implementing" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
